To propose a new idea:

1) Create new "issue" in the respective GitLab project, and describe it a text format, a video link or picture/diagram. If the idea is a concept or a specific design, feel free to upload sketches or basic 3d drawings. If an idea is not related to engineering, feel free to use whichever format is best.

2) Tag a senior team member to initiate a discussion and integrate the idea into the lifecycle

3) Once discussed, a new directory will be created by a senior team member for that specific idea, named and numberred accordingly. Example: project repository -> 1.Idea -> Active -> "



